 complianceconnectorfiduciary plan reviewconnectorplan effectivenessinvestment guidancefar too often retirement plans include highcost actively managed funds we believe in a passive approach that reduces costs and helps participants reach retirement more efficiently connectorinvestment reportingconnectorasset allocation — risk based modelsconnectortarget dated fundsconnectorquarterly statementseducationwe want to provide each participant with the information needed to live comfortably in retirement we value education at our firm and believe it is necessary for all participants to have an understanding of what is going on in the plan connectorenrollment process guidanceconnectoroneonone with a cfp® professionalconnectorretirement needs analysisconnectoreducation reviewsprovider services  benchmarkingit is necessary to compare costs each year to peer groups that are similar to your plan we provide a recordkeeping service through ascensus® but it is your decision as to which service provider you would like to use connectorcost analysis — upfront and ongoingconnectorparticipant service helpdeskconnectorplan illustrator reportingconnectorexecutive team reviews type and press “enter” to search happy almost new year  landmark financial advisors landmark financial advisors navigation client login wealth management experience retirement plan services divorcerelated financial planning landmark direct our team our thoughts blog articles newsletters privacy policy  adv brochure contact home search happy almost new year in uncategorized by landmark financial advisors llcdecember   comments wishing all a prosperous and blessed start to   the following is a timely poem by art cashin ‘tis the day before new year’s and despite what you’re hopin’ the folks in the boardroom say “the full day we’re open” so we’ll buy and we’ll sell as the tape crawls along and though “bubbly’s” verboten we may still sing a song two thousand fourteen was okay not really a wow till a santa claus rally to